Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.78,0:24:29.20,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\b1\pos(1000,700)\blur1\bord0\an4} alucardnoyuuutsu \N Anonymous{trumann#7436} \N Ziusudra \N Perevodildo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Anywhere our High Collar Lady goes, she gets herself in a tangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.15,0:01:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after hearing Shinobu's tearful story,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact he showed what seems \Nto be grandmother complex
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.33,0:01:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,only made her decision firmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, in order to support \NTamaki's one-sided love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.05,0:01:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio decided to make a farce out of her marriage apprenticeship to break her betrothal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would the goddess of fortune smile to?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:50.81,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,300)\c&HF4EDE5&\pos(720,240)\bord0\blur1\fs50\b1}Episode 6:\N {\fs90}A Fleeting Wedding March.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Howdy there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Shinobu's nanny?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Benio for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-oh? Your face's pale blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady, that look...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the big fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I dolled myself up to celebrate \Nan unreasonably demanding occasion of this kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We, as nobles, are taught \Nto keep composure at all times...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, we need to talk.\NPlease follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kisaragi, we humbly beg you to forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been tough to raise her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha squeaking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go! Go-go-go-go-go!\NGet outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, whaddya think ya are, \Nstopping in the middle of the entryway!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, oh well, if it's a bother,\Nfeel free to make a detour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like ya don't know \Nwho the hell ya talkin' to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Boss Benio's top henchman,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the one and only Ushigorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As my duty is to drive Lady Benio and Young Master to places.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio... and Young Master... that means...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sublieutenant Ijuuin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It can indeed be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss is in danger of overthrow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, Father,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't need to be this formal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is the only promise that I had made\Nto your mother before she passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A white mourning dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It symbolizes the vow that a woman makes \Nnot to marry a second time ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But why are you showing me this \Nall of a sudden, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother didn't need to wear this dress,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're going to marry a soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so, if something tragic happens, \Nyou'll have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get married again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you guess by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me if Shinobu died
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you would start a new life with another man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, I haven't even got married yet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're already talking about\Nwidowhood and such!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,very soon you'll become a member\Nof the Ijuuin family, so you will seldom visit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,About Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is damning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still clinging to the pathway like a tick!\NTake this! Just scram! {kind of hard to figure out}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?\NThis is a luxurious foreign car! Salt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing? Isn't it obvious? You're trying to kidnap my Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Kidnap? How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you blabbering about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, you've got the guts, you shrimp. Wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have any complaint,\NI, Ushigorou, am ready to retaliate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Salty...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you can accomplish \Nagainst my Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Taste that snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't take you long to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Exhaust gas, I didn't predict this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just end up married if I don't do anything, \Nbut I don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone begs me to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, what are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, so, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you're getting married, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unfair! It's so unfair!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, dummy!\NI won't let myself get married that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back home in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can guarantee you they'll kick me out right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, what's that look for...\NStarting a call girl biz? {デリヘル}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Call girl biz?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, you don't need to worry that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just apprenticeship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,After being evicted, I'll go home very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Benio,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,if everything goes well, after being back home,\Nyou could be my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What, Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... ouch, ow-ow-ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, I can cook your favourite grilled chicken,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,all kind of dishes, I'll be a top-notch chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this conversation's going all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,would you become my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I... don't know how to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Nanny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time to head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Nanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go. See you, Ranmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It somehow looks like she'll be gone forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so depressing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you sure are annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, if Benio doesn't come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi, I have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Anchin missed Princess Kiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,she went crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaoya Oshichi was lovesick too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Onatsu Kyouran too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There he goes again,\Nnot telling reality and fiction apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Take good care, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't be so sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be kicked out in no time, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny, look after Father, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady, take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Tamaki, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is a beautiful day, aren't you going outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was walking past here, so I thought of stopping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Such wonderful flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They smell so nicely...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any special occasion, madam?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu's fiancée is coming over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's for Benio...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I mean, is it for Lady Hanamura Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,she's your classmate, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I can imagine you know her rather well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we're close friends, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, could you tell me how the young lady is like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it is going to take,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll act as rude as humanly possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's very kind, also...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:22.32,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2218AB&\3c&HF2E2DD&}Boss Benio's car
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,wait for me, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and her acquaintances are wonderful people too...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's pulling that rickshaw over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my henchman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Henchman??
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Any complaints?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she, of all people, the chosen one to marry the poor Young Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from this shocked expression...\NI'm already leading, it's 1-0!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehehehe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Until marriage, I'll do what it takes for her to be taught properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be cheering for you\Nin your engagement-breaking mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still far from the Ijuuins' residence, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we're already inside the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't this just a forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,this is part of the estate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the mansion is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A castle!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, I had no idea they were this rich...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do your best, for my sake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Go-go-go-go! Boss!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Benio's faithful henchman, {I don't really understand what she says}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,he could be a decisive hand on this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, stop-stop-stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't stand mutts at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at my face, I don't mean threat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you didn't look threatening, \Nothers wouldn't feel threatened, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tamaki! Enough laughing,\NI may be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,These dogs are the Ijuuins' most faithful guard dogs,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't take strangers lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Boss Benio's most faithful guard, aren't I!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:15:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,let's negotiate, shall we? \NWhat I'm trying to say is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.47,0:16:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we're like the same pack of dogs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do something about it, Tamaki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time \Nthat I've seen Ushigorou so frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, shall I escort you to the mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady, you may come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddya think of the young lad...{I don't know}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I needa young lad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep cool, we are on the same side!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki, please do something, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenmaru, Chimaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,this man might look threatening,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but in reality it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a wrong impression!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you complimenting me or making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, these dogs are actually very smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd be eager to see you introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, introducing myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me out, hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it short.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the great Musashi, I was born in Hanakawado, on the district of Asakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I took an oath of serving Boss Benio,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the one and only Ushigorou,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,don't misjudge me, don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it easy, take it easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,H-e-l-p me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Shinobu is still busy and hasn't come back yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so please wait here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, how splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Clean as a new pin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I went a little overboard with this style.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, who cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My goal is to act unsavory,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and get properly kicked out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,no need to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a cigar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love a box like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing??
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you must be my stand-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I work here as a chef assistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's soon the time for my wedding, \Nso I'll have to resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're my stand-in, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The kitchen is right in this direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...that you think that I look like a chef assistant, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what the hell are you doing!? \NYou sicken me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange act...  {apparently, the Japanese script has an extra sentence Alucard didn't get in the Italian script (Ziu)}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, get a grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I sure will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to this misunderstanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I now feel fully confident!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so flat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my confidence already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there sure is nobody dwelling there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this is what kept company to Shinobu as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl is Young Master's future wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have the look of the position!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.91,0:20:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad for Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.82,0:20:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is such an old mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this strange sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... getting closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if this is an old place,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it can't be... a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, it's good craftsmanship,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,en garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:21:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Made in Japan" armors can speak too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it moves its eyes too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.15,0:22:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see if it's ticklish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu has another playfellow! \NIs he still on service?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, enough games! {dunno}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.63,0:22:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to teach you a lesson, get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Our High Collar Lady is about to get acquainted \Nwith a rusty lance...{Idk I don't get it so I put it by feel, the narrator isn't even speaking in the ITA version, they made characters speak lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of foe wields it?{敵もさるもの}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,An armored warrior appeared before Benio,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.45,0:23:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but the man under the helmet \Nis none other than Count Ijuuin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.43,0:23:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, an intrepid Samurai of Satsuma! {I'm sorry this part is just difficult}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He took a dislike to Benio from the get-go. {or something like this, he says はじめの出会いから[わるか？]}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As a problem can hide another,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the High Collar-style \Nengagement-breaking mission takes on water!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Here Comes the High Collar Lady:\NCount, Forgive me! Don't miss it!
